  m_Text: 'This tool creates a 3D city from your code base. Streets are generated
    from namespaces. Each building represents a class.

    Building size represents
    number of lines of code.

    Height represents number of functions.

    Color
    is a composite of dependencies / efferent coupling (R), dependants / afferent
    coupling (G), and complexity (B)


    Currently supports Java, ActionScript,
    C#.


    Input the path of your source code root directory:

'
